Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是怎么知道的  杰弗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And how would you know that, Jeff?
