Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是因為我們的分析人員發現了同樣的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know that because our analysis came up with the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就我所知  只有兩種可能情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, there are only two scenarios, as far as I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種是加布里爾去了文德爾酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The first is that Gabriel went to the Windall Hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有計劃有預謀地殘害了那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}sentient and premeditated, and killed those men in cold blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒唐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有什么可能的動機嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What motive could he possibly have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Until five years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈奇上校還是中央司令部的副指揮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Colonel Hatcher was the Deputy Commander of CENTCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟買襲擊后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, he led the response team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他指揮的應急小隊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}after the attack in Mumbai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他讓殺害加布里爾妻子的兇手逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He let the man who killed Gabriel's wife escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個動機充分嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How's that for motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說有兩種情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said there were two scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一種是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯片被黑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The chip was hacked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾受到他人的遠程操縱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Gabriel was operated remotely by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯片不能控制他做出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The chip can't make him do things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時不會做的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that he wouldn't normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人服了安眠藥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some people take a sleeping pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后半夜起床做出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}get up in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種他們平時不會做的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}do all sorts of things they wouldn't normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們并沒受到遠程操縱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they're not remotely operated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾不是機器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabriel is not a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為計劃中的芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Because the proposed chip
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用的是先進的光遺傳學技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"would utilize advanced optogenetics
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將電腦代碼轉換成大腦信號再轉換回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"to convert computer code to brain signals and back again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總會有惡意侵入引起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"there will always be a risk that a malicious hack
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分裂式大腦活動的風險\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}could enable a dissociated cerebral action."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通俗來說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In colloquial terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上  主體是可以被遠程操縱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the subject could, in theory, be remotely operated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段話記錄在十年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was written 10 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一篇名叫"論發條計劃的前景"的機密報告中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in a classified report entitled "The Potential of Clockwork"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者是希恩多·卡西迪博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by Dr. Shenandoah Cassidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我解釋下  什么叫分裂式大腦活動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Explain to me what a dissociated cerebral action is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于大腦特定區域向人類意識的信號堵塞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A hallucination whereby signals are blocked from certain areas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而產生的幻覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the brain to the conscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芯片被黑  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But this notion that the chip could be hacked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致加布里爾被迫實施謀殺的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Gabriel could be made to commit a murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在科學上是不可能的  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's scientifically impossible, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對付的到底是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個項目仍在測試中  莉莉安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The program is still in beta, Lillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每天都在學習了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're learning things every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被別人控制了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is he under someone else's control?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道我們有異常堅固的防火墻 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll recall we built a very robust firewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要避重就輕  回答我的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有一定的可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's within the realm of possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  我們現在還不能確定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The truth is, we just can't know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我知道你現在也很難過  尼爾特工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry. I know that must've been hard for you, Agent Neal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難過的是看到忠誠的缺乏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's hard is seeing how little loyalty there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠誠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個有趣的詞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's an interesting word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它對你意味著什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does it mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持  奉獻  承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Support. Dedication. Commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特勤局那句話怎么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that saying at the secret service?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九成精力保護當事人  一成精力解決問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}90% to the client, 10% to the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All due respect, Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并沒有把加布里爾看成我的當事人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't consider Gabriel my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的搭檔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I consider him my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的對面曾坐著很多不愿坦白的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've sat across from a lot of men who weren't willing to confess,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最終  他們都醒悟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but eventually, they all come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這里不是吉布提的黑獄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except this isn't some black site in Djibouti
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也不是一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm not an 18-year-old kid
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你拘留兩周的18歲小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you dropped in a hole for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得現在耍小聰明能救你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think your parlor tricks are gonna save you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我沒覺得  但我確定一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't... But I do know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的檔案來看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Judging from your files,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我更有嫌疑  實施這場謀殺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're more likely to have committed this murder than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道當莉莉安第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know that when Lillian first brought your file to me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我把你的檔案拿給總統時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and asked me to take it to the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就表示了深深的質疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had serious doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的經驗和英勇顯然不是問題所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your experience and bravery certainly weren't in question,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是你很年輕  而且是位女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you were young and you were a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心你倆間會有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had concerns about the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生情感聯系的可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of an emotional bond forming between the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安險些跟我翻臉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lillian nearly took my head off,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我是性別歧視主義\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}said I was being sexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I also had concerns
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺掉你繼父的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about the fact that you killed your stepfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是我母親的男友而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was my mother's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只有15歲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were 15 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻毫不猶豫地打死了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}yet you didn't hesitate to put him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不對  -不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Not true. - It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猶豫了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以第一槍打偏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why the first bullet missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個錯誤我沒有犯過第二次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never made the same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時你聲稱是正當防衛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the time, you claimed it was self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本來就是  -其實\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It was. - Truth is...
