Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不少追蹤逃亡者的訓練\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plenty of practice hunting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我把這事弄清前  別被抓到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep out of sight till I can figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我們把這事弄清前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Until we figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得回去  萊利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're going back, Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回哪去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要抓的是我  不是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the one they want, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興我為你工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it's a good thing I don't work for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就必須服從你的傻命令了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}otherwise, I'd have to follow your dumb orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算毀了你的前程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not gonna let you throw your career away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剛把我逃跑開出來的車藏起來之后嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As we cover up the getaway car I just drove?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不后悔  -真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I have no regrets. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本是保護總統的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You went from protecting the president
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻和一個失靈的機器人四處逃亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to riding in blind with a malfunctioning robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人不會痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Robots don't say "Ow."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是個殺人犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼看到了  我在錄像里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw what I saw. I'm on that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個構劃精巧的陰謀而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is a very sophisticated frame job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都明白這點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We both know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們至少得考慮一下可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we at least have to consider the possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚的事我一點也不記得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't remember anything from that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們都知道芯片并不可靠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we both know the chip can be unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you are not the chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最...信任的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A man I trust more than... any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里根總統\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, President Reagan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在華盛頓希爾頓酒店被槍擊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he was shot at the Washington Hilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個月之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And for months afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人一直在事發地點徘徊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there was a man who paced the sidewalk where it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是調查那個案件的特勤局特工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was a secret service agent who was investigating the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想揭開真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we want to figure out the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個地方可去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there's only one place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發現場\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去文德爾酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to go to the Windall Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}利蘭·斯特蘭德宅邸\N華盛頓特區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波旁酒最大的優點就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, one of the nice things about bourbon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定要喝下  才能體會其香醇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is you don't actually have to drink it to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時  只是拿在手里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes just holding it in your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是種享受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can be comfort enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  你還能做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plus, what else do you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我停職是個錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Removing me was a mistake. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人比我更了解加布里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody knows Gabriel like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把他安全的帶回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can bring him back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得到什么消息了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在騙我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實話實說  我是不是被開除了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Truth, dad. Am I out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不確定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not clear yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發條計劃一直都很脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Clockwork program's always been vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于幾個知情人來說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For those in the know, 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個科學技術本身就很可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the science is frightening,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的力量更是驚人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the power is breathtaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預算也是個天文數字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the budget's astronomical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些讓你成為了他們的眼中釘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That all adds up to a target on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這是泰塔祖的私仇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, this is personal with Tetazoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始他就想接管發條計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's been out to get Clockwork since day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再糾結過去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get up off the ground already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  我不是來找你上課的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, dad, I didn't come here for a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:19:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I came here --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要個擁抱嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You need a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要擁抱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't need a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  那就開始按我教給你的做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. Then start doing what I taught you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么干  他們已經開除我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How? They kicked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣  他們困住你手腳了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So what? Did they give you a lobotomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問個問題不需要許可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't need permission to ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這不是正在問嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有  至少沒有問到點子上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you're not. Not the right ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你離加布里爾和發條計劃太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're too close to Gabriel and Clockwork
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到全局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to see past any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標在遠處\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the other side of it is your real target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是你的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's where your brass ring is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真兇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個曾經能夠獲取\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A former military intelligence officer 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最敏感的中東情報的前軍方情報官員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who once had access to our most sensitive middle east intel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要和我們的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has an off-book meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦調查局副局長私下會面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the deputy director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得找個交通工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to find a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面包車可算不上是交通工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A minivan is not a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看窗戶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星控制系統  你的芯片可以控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's an on-sat system. You can chip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要偷這輛車\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You really want to steal this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是借用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就我們今天犯下的罪行里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, you know, on the list of felonies 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俠盜飛車 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that we've committed today, 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以算是最微不足道的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grand Theft Auto, it's way at the bottom.
