Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.38,0:35:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八十年代初  在他給中央司令部搞情報之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back in the early '80s before he ran intel for Centcom,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.80,0:35:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈奇還是個在國防情報局的外勤小特工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hatcher was a field agent with Defense Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.46,0:35:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對"漫布"著了迷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He apparently became fixated on the Flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.79,0:35:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.26,0:35:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就像是尼斯湖水怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the Loch Ness Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.56,0:35:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腳野人  外星人綁架\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}bigfoot, alien abductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.46,0:35:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是眾多傳說中的一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a legend, like any other,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.49,0:35:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古老的幽靈在昏暗嗆人的屋子里低語的那種\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whispered in dark, smoky rooms by old spooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.30,0:35:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們就和幽靈呆在一個昏暗嗆人的屋子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guess we're in a dark, smoky room with an old spook.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.56,0:35:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.51,0:35:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在1979年的伊朗人質危機之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}During the Iran Hostage Crisis in 1979,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.85,0:35:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始從薩瓦馬[前伊朗情報機構]\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we started hearing rumblings of a crazy idea
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.20,0:35:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到很多瘋狂的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}bubbling up through the Iranian Savama.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這后來成為了他們情報單位的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was the name of their intelligence agency then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.15,0:35:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的想法是向美國植入潛伏特工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The idea was to insert sleeper agents in U.S. society.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.73,0:35:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像蘇聯人那樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like the soviets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.88,0:35:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個關鍵的區別\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With one key difference --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.34,0:35:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招募方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}recruitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.93,0:35:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇聯人只對境內招募\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The soviets always recruited from within their borders
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.81,0:36:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并試圖教育自己的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and attempted to teach their people
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.45,0:36:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何融入我們的社會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how to blend in with our society,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.81,0:36:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這通常會帶來災難性的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}often with disastrous results.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.99,0:36:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照推測  伊朗人有個新奇的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Supposedly, the Iranians had a novel idea --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.35,0:36:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美國本土招募特工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}recruit in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.00,0:36:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到那些同情伊朗的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find people who either were sympathetic to Iran
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.78,0:36:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是那些可以用錢買通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or who could be made sympathetic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.26,0:36:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們同情伊朗的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by fulfilling certain financial needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.81,0:36:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終實現了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did it ever come to fruition?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.79,0:36:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.85,0:36:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果哈奇找到了這個神話的證據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what if Hatcher found proof of this myth
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.42,0:36:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這給他帶來殺身之禍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it got him killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.18,0:36:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也殃及到了他要把證據移交給的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}along with the deputy director of the FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.19,0:36:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦調查局副局長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he was turning it over to?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這是個重大突破\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd say that's a big leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.06,0:36:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的職責就是尋找突破  你教我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're in the business of big leaps. You taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.46,0:36:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把我的人和美辰一起帶來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna bring my people in along with Mei Chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.57,0:36:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會合作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She won't cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓她合作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll make her cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.83,0:36:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小公雞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rooster...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.90,0:36:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小心點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.81,0:37:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.97,0:37:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來她是按約一個人來的  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like she came alone like we agreed. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.86,0:37:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, how do you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.65,0:37:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟緊  盯著她  我去和莉莉安說句話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay close, keep an eye on her. I'll check in with Lillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.72,0:37:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你犯了個可悲的錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're making a tragic mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.65,0:37:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得你是他們的一員  但你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think you're one of them. You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.75,0:37:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對他們而言只是個硬件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're just a piece of hardware to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.40,0:37:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本不用那么孤單的  你自己選擇的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You didn't have to be so alone. You made that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.88,0:37:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.27,0:37:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人替我做了選擇  把它放在我腦袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone else made a choice to put this in my head --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.51,0:37:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你英明神武的卡西迪博士  記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your heroic Dr. Cassidy, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.43,0:37:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他選擇了救自己的命  代價就是我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He chose to save his own life at the expense of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.19,0:37:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭腦都被你引以為傲的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your mind is spinning along with that uniquely American
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.12,0:37:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典型美式道德羅盤束縛住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}moral compass you're all so proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.18,0:37:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's enough. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.58,0:37:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她不是一個人  -閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She's not alone. - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.56,0:37:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個陷阱  加布里爾  看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a trap, Gabriel. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.98,0:37:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒察覺到任何無線電廣播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not picking up any radio transmissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.58,0:37:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.68,0:38:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她了解你的  知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She knows you. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.86,0:38:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺不對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.88,0:38:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.47,0:38:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到那個狙擊手  活捉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find that shooter! I want him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.90,0:38:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算計我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were set up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.88,0:38:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.82,0:38:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他們走  你為什么要殺他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Call them off! Why are you shooting at him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.73,0:38:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That wasn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.84,0:38:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指望我相信嗎  叫他們走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You expect me to believe that? Call them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.76,0:38:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們干的  莉莉安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't us, Lillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.21,0:38:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒道理  為什么莉莉安會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doesn't make any sense. Why would Lillian --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.83,0:38:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他快不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.88,0:38:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會撐住的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.30,0:38:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  我們正在搜尋屋頂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're checking rooftops right now, sir. 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.69,0:38:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有狙擊手痕跡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No sign of the shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.74,0:39:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-加布里爾呢  -也沒有  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What about Gabriel? - Negative, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.26,0:39:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到他們  記住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find them. Remember -- 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.53,0:39:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用無線電和電子設備  去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no radios, nothing electronic. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.95,0:39:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾  加布里爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabriel. Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.77,0:39:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能待在這兒  這不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't stay here. It's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.35,0:39:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.95,0:39:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道他們會向我們開火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you know they'd fire on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.29,0:39:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒明白  是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.69,0:39:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共開了兩槍  第二槍是射向你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were two shots fired. The last one was meant for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.13,0:39:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.64,0:39:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道政府為什么要背叛你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did I know the government would turn on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.67,0:39:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是誰雇我來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who do you think hired me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.94,0:39:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人雇我來殺了那些人  然后栽贓給你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was hired to kill those men and frame you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.64,0:39:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的政府雇的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hired by your own government.
