Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.12,0:39:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比你能想象的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is bigger and more insidious
